    Scope and Contents
These records consist of official records (agendas and minutes), working papers (correspondence, memos, reports, announcements and notes) of various Faculty Senate Ad Hoc and Subcommittees from 1972 to 1994.  Committees include but are not limited to Election committees, Ad Hoc Committee on the Status of University Women, Task Force on Sexual Harassment Policy, and Ad Hoc Committee on Governance.  
  
